<HEADLINE> Shanghai University Co-operates with Local Enterprises </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 26 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Jiaotong University
signed an agreement here today on jointly establishing a real
estate company together with three local enterprises.
</P>
<P>
This is another phase of cooperation between Shanghai's
universities and large enterprises, following one between the
Shanghai Xinhuangpu (Group) Co. and Fudan University.
</P>
<P>
With a registered capital of 150 million yuan, The new company,
the Shanghai Residence Science and Technological Investment
Co. Ltd., expected to take advantage of the university's strength
in technology for updating the quality of Shanghai's residential
construction.
</P>
<P>
The three enterprises also sold 500 apartments to Shanghai
Jiaotong University at a discount price, which will be used to
improve the university's teachers' living conditions. 
